text = "Story

Somewhere deep in the South Pole, there once was a great penguin colony.
They lived happily, but they had to avoid the leopard seals that also lived near their home.
Then one day it happened: the leopard seals were becoming more numerous and larger, 
there was only one way to still their hunger. When they attacked, the penguins 
had no chance of survival. Only a few penguins survived, 
they began to leave their home in search of a safer place to live. Just one penguin 
decided to stay, because she found eight little baby penguins who could not escape 
on their own yet. She made a home for them and swore to care and provide for them 
as long as she could, until they could look after themselves.
Every day, she locks the little ones in their home and goes hunting for fish. 
But great danger awaits her, since the leopard seals are still out there…"

